org.opendaylight.controller.protocol_plugin.openflow.internal

Class ReadServiceFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.protocol_plugin.openflow.internal.ReadServiceFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IOFStatisticsListener, IReadServiceFilter, IContainerAware, IContainerListener

    public class ReadServiceFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements IReadServiceFilter, IContainerListener, IOFStatisticsListener, IContainerAware
    Read Service shim layer which is in charge of filtering the flow statistics based on container. It is a Global instance.
